-- Nitesh Estates Acquires Rights to Develop Luxury Residences in Bangalore
-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 2010-09-21T04:21:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/nitesh-estates-acquires-rights-to-develop-luxury-residences-in-bangalore.html
Nitesh Estates Ltd. acquired joint
rights to develop a property in Bangalore, according to a
statement on the Bombay Stock Exchange today.  Nitesh plans to develop luxury residences on the property
at a cost of 1 billion rupees, the statement said. 